+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Watchbill shape conformance
+    Given a watchbill.json file is present
+    Then the watchbill has valid schema and required fields
+    And the watchbill contains only scenario references that exist in specs
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Perturbation quiescence
+    Given the implementation code is scanned
+    Then no PERTURBATION token is found in any production source file
+    And the perturbation message is absent from a green tree
